{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10110447289284-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10110447289284-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100137048388-1","P_10100137048388-2"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":4,"description":"阅读课外文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":600,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>如何让手机支付更安全</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">设置手机开机密码或SIM卡绑定手机开机密码。在手机中安装加密软件，对移动支付软件增加一层密码，这样，即便有人破解了开机密码，支付软件仍有密码保护。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">取消手机号作为用户名登录支付宝，使用专用的邮箱登录。这样就可以确保盗窃或者拾到手机的人不知道该手机绑定的支付宝账号。不建议使用QQ邮箱，因为手机QQ多被设置为自动登录，可以轻易通过QQ进入邮箱。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">给手机中的支付工具设置单独、高安全级别的密码，切勿和锁屏密码相同。登录密码和支付密码也要设置不同的。如果邮箱、社交网站（如微博、人人网、开心网等）等登录名和支付账号名一致，要保证密码不同。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">使用数字证书、宝令、支付盾、手机动态口令等安全产品。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">如果手机丢失，立即打电话给银行和第三方支付供应商冻结相关业务，找手机运营商挂失手机号码并补办。可以在电脑上登录支付宝等账号，关闭无线支付业务。万一发生账户资金被盗用的情况，立刻拨打110报警。</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"手机支付的密码设置要求是__$$__ __$$__ __$$__。（按原文内容先后顺序）","answers":[{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"2","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":